lore: In the heart of Demacia, our summoner found solace in the regimented life of the city's rigorous training grounds. Their self-direction, a beacon amidst the rigid conformity, led them to forge alliances with like-minded individuals. The stimulation of battle, a stark contrast to the monotonous drills, fueled their passion for the art of war. Yet, their unconventional methods, though effective, raised eyebrows among the traditionalist council. The summoner's journey was just beginning, and the trials ahead would test their resolve.
reflection: Improve CS/min by practicing last hitting in custom games and focusing on securing CS in lane during lulls in enemy engagement.
